snippet.title: RPG Maker MZ Trailer #1
snippet.description:
In our first RPG Maker MZ trailer, we're taking a quick look at the map editor, event editor, and character generator! What new features do you spot?

RPG Maker MZ, going live this summer, learn more on our site or on Steam!

https://www.rpgmakerweb.com/a/comingsoon/rpg-maker-mz
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1096900/RPG_Maker_MZ/
